# Active Tasks

Index of current work items and their status.

## Task Claiming Protocol

1. Find an `[AVAILABLE]` task below
2. Update frontmatter: Change status to `[CLAIMED by @your-id]`
3. Commit and push immediately
4. Create feature branch: `git checkout -b feature/task-description`
5. Work on task following Plan → Act → Test workflow
6. Mark `[COMPLETED]` when done

